p: As shown above, the efficacy of the different compounds has also evidenced a concentration-dependent effect, as the best efficacy values were found with the highest concentrations of both treatments. In this sense, the concentration of 57.1 µM of IVM plus 82.80 mg/mL of OFIEOH, and 200 mg/mL of OFIEOH plus 25.7 µM of IVM, had the highest effect on L3 motility ( Table 4 and Table 5).
